  <name>Image Background Remover</name>
  <summary>Automatically remove backgrounds from photos and images using on-device AI</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Image Background Remover is a desktop application for quickly and accurately removing
      backgrounds from images. It provides a one-click workflow for single images and
      a batch mode for processing multiple photos. The application is designed for
      photographers, designers, and anyone who needs transparent PNGs or isolated subjects.
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Automatic subject detection with AI-powered matting for clean edges</li>
      <li>Supports common image formats: PNG, JPEG, WEBP</li>
      <li>Batch processing and drag-and-drop workflow</li>
      <li>Preserves alpha channel and offers optional feathering and edge smoothing</li>
      <li>Command-line mode for automation and integration into scripts</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      The tool is optimized for accuracy and speed on modern desktops and can be used
      entirely offline once installed.
    </p>
  </description>

